text: Kot Rajput is a town located in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is located in Lahore District at 31°9'0N 73°13'0E with an altitude of 173 metres (570 feet).Location of Kot Rajput - Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Kutruwal and Bhagthal. ==References== Category:Populated places in Lahore District Category:History of Pakistan
